{"tid":2393321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屯門豐景園第一座被劃為指定受限區域居民需強檢","createTime":"2021-02-03T11:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T11:16:55.000Z","uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3dce64a3d2adc962115e075686d9a077a12feb45","tid":2393321,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:14:07.000Z","msg":"政府再突襲式封區，晚上7時宣布，即時起將屯門海珠路7號豐景園第一座，劃為指定「受限區域」，區域內的人須留在處所，並按政府安排接受強制檢測，直至所有人完成檢測，方可離開。<br />\n<br />\n政府將設立臨時採樣站，受檢人士要在明日凌晨2時前前接受檢測，目標是早上約7時解封。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2377666/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E8%B1%90%E6%99%AF%E5%9C%92%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%83%E7%82%BA%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2377666%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%2599%25AF%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259F%259F%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%25AA%25A2&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=16a1dce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2377666/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E8%B1%90%E6%99%AF%E5%9C%92%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%83%E7%82%BA%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2</a>"},{"pid":"8bbca763d382a3ef154929f00049578ec4ecf13c","tid":2393321,"uid":225380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050b7ba9dec3e460366f56a69e40ea13389d3e1f","tid":2393321,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bbca763d382a3ef154929f00049578ec4ecf13c","tid":2393321,"uid":225380,"like":0